welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Hutto, a charming city known for its small-town feel and friendly community. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our city has to offer. Happy exploring!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Austin Executive Airport serves all commercial flights and houses various amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Austin Executive Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a luxurious and exclusive experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Austin-bergstrom International Airport houses all the major airlines and provides a variety of services and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: South Terminal
terminals.description: The South Terminal at Austin-bergstrom International Airport serves low-cost carriers and offers a more relaxed and intimate atmosphere for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
